From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ask2 PR14z19 <ask2@local>
Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 06:35:00 +0000
Subject: ask: wire fs_initcall to register pre-netdev hook

PR14z19 Path A stage 3. Now that the ASK2 source is built-in
(patch 0048), we replace module_init(ask_init) / module_exit(ask_exit)
with fs_initcall(ask_init). This guarantees ASK2 initializes after
subsys_initcall (which brings up BMan/QMan/FMan/PCD core) but before
device_initcall (which spawns dpaa_eth probing).

During fs_initcall, ask_init() now calls:
   fman_pcd_register_pre_netdev_hook(ask_pcd_install_hook);
to ensure we intercept MAC9/MAC10 probes to lay down our 
KG schemes before dpaa_eth falls back to its bypass logic.

Signed-off-by: ask2 PR14z19 <ask2@local>
